Issue #10 (Individual Issue) Cassis Lafleur
    Added option to delete saved games

Issue #18 (Individual Issue) Cassis Lafleur
    removed "rpg_" for start of every save game

	    How to test?
	1. Launch the game
	2. pick a resolution
	3. Start endless Campaign
	4. Chose Random Party
	5. Name the campaign
	6. Right click to bring up menu
	7. Select Quit Game
	8. Select Delete Saved Games options
	9. The Campaign you just named will be in the list
	This also test the fact the campaign does Not start with "rpg_"  (Issue 18)
	10.Click on it to delete it this will take you back to the main menu
	11. You can double check to make sure the campaign was deleted by selecting Delete Saves Games to see that its gone

