Issue #17 (Individual Issue) Cassis Lafleur
    Renaming saved games and still have the game consider them valid

	How to test
	1. Launch the game
	2. pick a resolution
	3. Start endless Campaign
	4. Chose Random Party
	5. Name the campaign
	6. Right click to bring up menu
	7. Select Quit Game
	8. Navigate to C:\Users\{User Name}\dmeternal or simulare if not on Windows
	9. This folder has the saved game file they end in .sav
	10.Rename your desired save file to what ever you want as long as you don't change the file extension
	11.go back to the game no your newly renamed save will show up in the "Load Campaign" and the "Delete Saved Games options"
